{"tid":466704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有食開既人先會明］人生的意義","createTime":"2017-11-12T20:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T15:37:28.000Z","uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84dfc80ecb8a8e3392183c564a6cbf0efc7dacfd","tid":466704,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T20:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電腦先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經過嘅你不妨花啲時下睇下呢段片<br />\n當你灰，絕望，孤單既時候<br />\n會諗人究竟為左啲乜生存係呢嗰世上<br />\n你好想去搵答案但一直搵唔到<br />\n所以不如學會從中享受...<br />\n而慢慢你會發現呢嗰世界其實仲有好多𡃁嘅嘢你仲未欣賞過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i97T0NYSio0?list=PLQlyXM5uz8D55UovhvcSwvYUrwS5kvqKz&amp;t=5076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi97T0NYSio0%3Flist%3DPLQlyXM5uz8D55UovhvcSwvYUrwS5kvqKz%26t%3D5076&d=ToY5HEM1M9s7pBlllVuXYl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c12e0ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i97T0NYSio0?list=PLQlyXM5uz8D55UovhvcSwvYUrwS5kvqKz&amp;t=5076</a><br />\n<br />\n由1:24:36－1:27:49睇<br />\n我次次都可以重播3/4次咁睇<br />\n中意既可以較1.25速睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完有種被治癒嘅感覺<br />\n同埋好想去睇曬呢嗰世界佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2547da2bc77f4053c3dd1c6214219cbed80e26d","tid":466704,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T20:46:31.000Z","msg":"There are more things in heaven and earth, Horatio, than are dreamt of in your philosophy. (Hamlet 1.5)<br />\n天地之間有許多事情，是你的睿智所無法想像的。&mdash;&mdash;《哈姆雷特》<br />\n/在這天地間有許多事情是人類哲學所不能解釋的。"},{"pid":"3404817218ba903520ee308bcbb1489425d01642","tid":466704,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T20:52:08.000Z","msg":"The time of life is short ； to spend that shortness basely， it would be too long 。<br />\n人生苦短，若虛度年華，則短暫的人生就太長了。"},{"pid":"b6d5a8706146f5ce706ebf445c92cbb192866d9a","tid":466704,"uid":17270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T21:05:29.000Z","msg":"Lsd"},{"pid":"fa6e764f947a343cb4f60f65bc257d4961b86e9e","tid":466704,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lsd</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43bc7f1c8104543431754a28592f6172de5d731","tid":466704,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T21:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfe9c46e214ba8ebaa120e7af879de4584f7d57","tid":466704,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:44:14.000Z","msg":"UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc59f9734dcc7468368e38c429d07f6815cdc8a2","tid":466704,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}